│ 667 /// The idea is to run the vplan on a given loop twice, firstly to setup the        │
│ 668 /// skeleton and vectorize the main loop, and secondly to complete the skeleton     │
│ 669 /// from the first step and vectorize the epilogue.  This is achieved by            │
│ 670 /// deriving two concrete strategy classes from this base class and invoking        │
│ 671 /// them in succession from the loop vectorizer planner.                            │
